      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## What's New\r\n\r\n### Native List Editing in Columns\r\n- **Tab** indents list items (bullet, numbered, task) — numbered child items reset to `1.`\r\n- **Shift+Tab** unindents list items\r\n- **Enter** auto-continues lists (bullet, numbered, task); empty marker exits the list\r\n- Tab/Shift+Tab still navigate between columns when not on a list line\r\n\r\n### Ctrl+L Checkbox Toggle\r\n- **Ctrl/Cmd+L** toggles checkboxes inside column editors (previously affected the main document)\r\n- Supports custom task statuses (`[/]`, `[!]`, `[?]`, etc.) controlled by themes\r\n- Clicking task checkboxes in preview now toggles them correctly\r\n\r\n### List Spacing Fixes\r\n- Fixed extra vertical gaps between parent list items caused by inherited `white-space: pre-wrap`\r\n- List item line-height set to `1.4em` for comfortable multi-line reading\r\n- Blank lines between list items now render as visible gaps\r\n- Blank lines between block elements (paragraphs, headings, lists) also render as gaps\r\n\r\n### Third-Party Plugin Autocomplete\r\n- Column editors now bridge Obsidian's EditorSuggest API for third-party plugin suggestions (e.g. Iconize `:` trigger)",
